Hello, Bill.

01:12:31.973 --> 01:12:32.974
Hi, Mr. Bonham.

01:12:32.974 --> 01:12:33.983
Bill hasn't got a pole,

01:12:33.983 --> 01:12:35.918
and he's only here
for the afternoon.

01:12:35.918 --> 01:12:37.920
