was in the water.

01:14:55.774 --> 01:14:58.143
And, um-- we hunted
around for it,

01:14:58.143 --> 01:15:00.612
fished with the oars,
but--

01:15:01.013 --> 01:15:03.515
but we couldn't find it,
so it's gone.

01:15:26.839 --> 01:15:28.740
Well...

01:15:31.577 --> 01:15:34.021
Shouldn't let
a fishing pole...

01:15:35.422 --> 01:15:38.324
