01:19:07.351 --> 01:19:09.328
<i>I can tell when it's summer!</i>

01:19:09.328 --> 01:19:11.697
<i>I can smell leaves</i>
<i>burning in autumn.</i>

01:19:14.066 --> 01:19:16.435
<i>Oh, Merry Christmas,</i>
<i>sweet nurse.</i>

01:19:16.435 --> 01:19:19.371
<i>Merry Christmas to you.</i>

01:19:19.371 --> 01:19:20.872
<i>Merry Christmas,</i>
<i>and all my love!</i>

01:19:20.873 --> 01:19:23.383
<i>Merry, Merry,</i>
<i>Merry Christmas.</i>

01:19:23.593 --> 01:19:25.661
Merry Christmas!

